decision.option_label: Block access immediately on payment failure

messages.text: **Let me clarify:** This is about Better Uptime monitoring config. The docs say free tier = 3-min checks, but monitors are set to 1-min. Either monitors fail to create OR you get charged $20/mo unexpectedly. **Options:** (1) Change to 3-min = stay free, (2) Keep 1-min = pay $20/mo, (3) Skip = this is just a docs issue, not code. What would you like to do?
